T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"罰你打J三次, 要連續唔準睇AV"},{"pid":"30593ba0e78d07f23372cd1de19f79164d386b8d","tid":1331593,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】多名反對修訂《逃犯條例》的示威者在7月1日衝擊立法會後，據報到台灣尋求庇護。公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋擔心，若再有港人獲庇護，會影響香港的國際聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋早上出席一電台節目時解釋，若再有港人獲庇護，<span style=\"color: red;\">外界便會質疑香港的律政司有否作出公平檢控</span>。&lt;--<span style=\"font-size: large;\">姐係屌林奠老母</span><br />\n<br />\n他並表示，任何人尋求其他地方的政治庇護，是否獲批，得視乎申請人在原居地是否因為政治原因而受到檢控，或可能受到檢控，以及是否有機會得到不公平審訊。"},{"pid":"b3fcdff2f8e19fad61fe5de453b9d0d6f1707862","tid":1331593,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190718&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59837309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190718%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59837309&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=25e47d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190718%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59837309&h=5a2510ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190718&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59837309</a><br />\n<br />\n少部份警察都開始被銀髮族出黎感化啦.<br />\n開始搵返自己入警隊係點解"},{"pid":"98d186b838dcd7c98a71e489cc132a9cbfc549de","tid":1331593,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bda3804e8c1ecdfed3a0595d40e31e9df473cd6","tid":1331593,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bbde7f1581a949477819db2f2f144b4713ec3fb","tid":1331593,"uid":156254,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"95873f42a4032a78eee6f02d8fb39997685f1feb","tid":1331593,"uid":55130,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9559fcbf58131f3ff8d6deb5d28baa7fe2bde84a","tid":1331593,"uid":156254,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy